â€¢ Generates objects in a structure based on the data within.
â€¢ Place the block and open the GUI to set data. You can test your data with the Generate button.
info.structure_gel.default: â€¢ Spreads the gel along the cardinal directions, only replacing air.
info.structure_gel.diagonal_spread: â€¢ Spreads itself along the cardinal and diagonal directions. Useful to get around vines and other weird corners.
info.structure_gel.dynamic_spawner_descr:
â€¢ Behaves similar to a vanilla spawner, but uses pre-determined registered behaviors instead of storing spawning logic in the block itself. These behaviors must be registered by mods in code.
â€¢ Place the block and open the GUI to set data.

info.structure_gel.gunpowder: â€¢ Use gunpowder to destroy all connected gels.
info.structure_gel.photosensitive: â€¢ Only spreads the gel in positions not exposed to the sky. Great for rooms with open walls.
info.structure_gel.place: â€¢ Place while sneaking to trigger the spread effect.
info.structure_gel.unknown_behavior: â€¢ The behavior for this block is undefined. Make sure you're using or extending off of StructureGelBlock in code.
